N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4000.2 - Powers reserved

State Regulations

All powers of the commission not specifically defined
in this Subchapter are reserved to the commission under the laws creating the
commission and specifying the commission's powers and duties. Notes
